title: Looking Back: Are We Our True Selves Onscreen?
description:
Have you ever wondered what Rhett and Link are like when the cameras are turned off? Well, they already explained this! In this final throwback episode. Rhett and Link explain how the characters they play on GMM are similar to their real-life personalities, and also all the ways they aren't. Plus, Link tries to prove to his children that he's actually smart.
Originally aired 4/25/2019.
﻿If you want new episodes, be sure to follow Dispatches From Myrtle Beach, Link's new podcast with his dad! Available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, or wherever you get your podcasts!
﻿Don't miss the biggest Mythical live event of the year! Visit MythiConTickets.com for more info!
